&lt;p&gt;The FAVAR model is represented by the following system:&lt;/p&gt;
$$
X_t = \Lambda^f F_t + \Lambda^y Y_t + e_t 
$$$$
\begin{bmatrix} F_t \\ Y_t \end{bmatrix} = \Psi(L)\begin{bmatrix} F_{t-1} \\ Y_{t-1} \end{bmatrix} + v_t 
$$&lt;p&gt;where $F_t$ is the collection of variables that is unobservable, while $Y_t$ is is of the observable. For further description of the FAVAR model and its properties please see BBE (QJE, 2005)&lt;/p&gt;

